<p style="margin-left: 300px"><font size="5"><b> Symbols</b></p>
<p style="border:3px; border-style:solid; border-color:##808080; padding: 1em;margin-left: 300px; margin-right: 300px"><font size="4">Their most remarkable feature is their decorative

motifs, many of which remain enigmatic to this day. spirals, arcades, rosettes, vine leaves and grapes, suns and crescent moons are among the images that appear. Figural motifs include

processions of deer, dancing the kolo, hunting and, most famously, the image of the man with his right hand raised, perhaps in a gesture of fealty.</p>

